==Bog Biome Discoveries==
{{Explorer Note
| title = Biome Glitch Discovery Bog #1
| text = This biome is teeming with life --<br/>so much life that it’s making the simulation glitch out.<br/>Imagine what it takes to keep track of the insect swarms alone!<br/>Thousands of insects, each on its own flight path, each looking for something to consume.<br/>Hmmm. They’re rather like tiny versions of you survivors, aren’t they?
| author = HLN-A
| icon = NoteHLN-A.png
| sound = HLNA Glitch Biome Bog 01.ogg
}}

{{Explorer Note
| title = Biome Glitch Discovery Bog #2
| text = My sensors are picking up heaps of organic compounds in the air, just floating around.<br/>I reckon you’d call them smells?<br/>It’s just chemistry to me, mate.<br/>When you’re sniffing around this biome, watch out for hydrogen sulfide.<br/>You know, Aitch-two Ess? My data says it smells pungent, but then it deadens the human sense of smell.<br/>You can breathe in the poison without realizing it.
| author = HLN-A
| icon = NoteHLN-A.png
| sound = HLNA Glitch Biome Bog 02.ogg
