| text = Gravity: you don’t miss it ‘til it’s gone, eh?<br/>Or I reckon it’s not “gone” so much as it’s “on its way out the door.”<br/>Based on the data in that glitch, the lack of gravity should impact you in heaps of different ways.<br/>You can jump better, of course, and projectiles travel further.<br/>If you’re feeling clumsy, you can even fall off things without getting hurt.<br/>Not that I recommend it!
| author = HLN-A
| icon = NoteHLN-A.png
