| text = The Genesis simulation has hotter and colder places than here,<br/>but this biome is the only place where you’ll have hot and cold separated by just the border of a shadow.<br/>It’s one of the side effects of a proper atmosphere in the other biomes, I reckon --<br/>it evens out the temperature from place to place.<br/>Air: it’s good for more than just breathing!
| author = HLN-A
| icon = NoteHLN-A.png
| sound = HLNA Glitch Biome Moon 02.ogg
